article_title: Health insurance 'navigator' to speak at local event
article_text:
Jan Potter, patient navigator at Hutchinson Regional Medical Center, will be the featured speaker at a 6 p.m. Nov. 2 public forum at Interfaith Housing Services offices, 1326 E. Ave. A.
